The evidence with the title ''skyrocketing' premiums - factcheck.org ' says Apr 11, 2014  ... The line : premiums and health care costs are 'skyrocketing' under the Affordable Care Act . The party: Republican. Several anti-Obamacare ads have made the claim that premiums or health care costs have gone up under the law . And “ skyrocketing ” is the word of choice in these attack ads. 
